nodes.text: Jayeena was a pilot and veteran of the Battle of Endor. In the time following that battle, Jayeena often competed in Holosimulator combat scenarios against a less experienced pilot from the Bespin system, Zed. The pair also created their own combat simulator scenarios. One of their competitions resulted in the "Zed vs. Jayeena" holosimulator skirmish template.
The brief description of Jayeena does not specify if she served with the Empire or the Rebel Alliance in the Battle of Endor.
